\u00ednea, temperatura de tu cuerpo y salud de tu coraz\u00f3n.\nMeditaci\u00f3n\nNo hay mejor terapia para relajarte, que la\n[meditaci\u00f3n ](http://www.revistamoi.com/bienestar/beneficios-de-la-meditacion/)y el [mindfullness](http://www.revistamoi.com/bienestar/7-apps-para-practicar-el-mindfulness/). Para antes de dormir, medita 10-15 minutos para relajarte y cambiar tu mood. Igual, si te levantas en medio de la noche, la opci\u00f3n perfecta en meditar para volver a la relajaci\u00f3n.\n\u00bfTe gust\u00f3 esta nota? Calif\u00edcala", "language": null, "image": "https://www.revistamoi.com/wp-content/uploads/2017/05/insomnio.jpg", "pagetype": "article", "links": ["#", "/", "#", "https://www.revistamoi.com/category/pooor/", "https://www.revistamoi.com/category/amor-y-sexo/", null, "https://www.revistamoi.com/category/salud/", "https://www.revistamoi.com/category/nutricion/", "https://www.revistamoi.com/category/sube-godinez/", "https://www.revistamoi.com/category/sube-godinez/chamba/", "https://www.revistamoi.com/category/sube-godinez/varo/", "https://www.revistamoi.com/category/cucu/", "#", "https://www.revistamoi.com/category/bienestar/", "https://www.revistamoi.com/category/bienestar/lookcionario/", "https://www.revistamoi.com/category/bienestar/ifp/", "https://www.revistamoi.com/category/variedat/", "https://www.revistamoi.com/category/variedat/moiscotas/", "https://products.mmkgroup.com.mx/", "https://products.mmkgroup.com.mx/", "#login-form", null, "#", "https://twitter.com/revistamoi", "https://www.facebook.com/revistamoi/", "https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCRCdWBefL7f7w-GeQhBG5dA", "https://plus.google.com/+RevistamoiOficial", "https://www.instagram.com/revistamoi/", "https://es.pinterest.com/revistamoi/", "https://www.revistamoi.com/", "https://products.mmkgroup.com.mx/", "https://products.mmkgroup.com.mx/", "https://products.mmkgroup.com.mx/", "https://suscripciones.mmkgroup.com.mx/", "https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.mmkgroup.suscrip